{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/a3/ef/90497_crt_7IZoz.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a3/ef/90497_crt_7IZoz.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/a3/ef/90497_crt_7IZoz.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/a3/ef/90497_crt_7IZoz.jpg"},"name":"ポテト","summary":"虽然个性随和，但偶尔也会无视驾驶的指示。遇见需要帮忙的人就会挺身而出。喜欢吃胡萝卜。\r\n\r\nのんびり屋だけど運転手の操縦を時々無視する側面も。助けを求める者がいたら、どんな状況であっても行動を起こす勇敢さを持ち合わせる。ニンジンが好き。","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":90497},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/a1/84/90498_crt_ciC1c.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a1/84/90498_crt_ciC1c.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/a1/84/90498_crt_ciC1c.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/a1/84/90498_crt_ciC1c.jpg"},"name":"シロモ","summary":"在本来就很胆小的天竺鼠车车中，也是属于特别胆小的个性。\r\n喜欢对着温柔的驾驶撒娇，但也时常被卷入麻烦事中，十分崇拜如同大姊姊般的泰迪。\r\n喜欢吃生菜。\r\n\r\n基本的に臆病なモルカーのなかでも特に臆病な性格を持つ。心優しい運転手に甘えたりもするが、いろいろなトラブルに巻き込まれがち。テディを姉御のように慕う。レタスが好き。","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":90498},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/a4/a0/90499_crt_x8C2w.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a4/a0/90499_crt_x8C2w.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/a4/a0/90499_crt_x8C2w.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/a4/a0/90499_crt_x8C2w.jpg"},"name":"アビー","summary":"既认真又富有好奇心，虽然身上贴着新手驾驶标志，但总是期待着毕业的那天。\r\n相较于其他天竺鼠车车更有自尊心，很害怕猫。\r\n\r\n真面目で好奇心旺盛。初心者マークを付けているが、いつか卒業できる日を夢見ている。他のモルカーに比べてプライドが高い。猫が苦手。","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":90499},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/80/c0/90500_crt_PzCCT.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/80/c0/90500_crt_PzCCT.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/80/c0/90500_crt_PzCCT.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/80/c0/90500_crt_PzCCT.jpg"},"name":"チョコ","summary":"行为优雅又端庄，却有着意想不到的强大身体能力。\r\n喜欢把自己打扮得漂漂亮亮、也很关注流行趋势，梦想能成为世界第一的高级天竺鼠车车。\r\n\r\n爽やかでおしとやか、かと思いきや力強くて身体能力に特化した一面も。綺麗好きでオシャレにも気を遣っている。いつかNo１の高級モルカーになることが夢。","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":90500},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/6d/d9/90501_crt_dUlRO.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6d/d9/90501_crt_dUlRO.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/6d/d9/90501_crt_dUlRO.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/6d/d9/90501_crt_dUlRO.jpg"},"name":"テディ","summary":"总之就是什么都很爱吃、也很爱动。脱线的个性让它从来不会感到害怕。\r\n经常做出令人意想不到的事，是个总是害大家吓一跳的麻烦制造者。\r\n\r\nとにかく何でもよく食べ、よく動く。おてんばで怖気知らず。とんでもない行動をするトラブルメーカーで、周りからは恐れられている。","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":90501},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/50/87/114716_crt_hOOZ9.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/50/87/114716_crt_hOOZ9.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/50/87/114716_crt_hOOZ9.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/50/87/114716_crt_hOOZ9.jpg"},"name":"ローズ","summary":"オシャレに気を使っている。","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":114716},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/8b/0f/114717_crt_RUaOQ.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/8b/0f/114717_crt_RUaOQ.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/8b/0f/114717_crt_RUaOQ.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/8b/0f/114717_crt_RUaOQ.jpg"},"name":"ペーター","summary":"ポテトたちが訪れたドライビングスクールで教習を受ける新人モルカー。","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":114717},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/6c/2c/114718_crt_L2Kzq.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6c/2c/114718_crt_L2Kzq.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/6c/2c/114718_crt_L2Kzq.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/6c/2c/114718_crt_L2Kzq.jpg"},"name":"ひー","summary":"ポテトたちが訪れたドライビングスクールで働くモルカー。","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":114718},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/39/c5/114719_crt_AymAH.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/39/c5/114719_crt_AymAH.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/39/c5/114719_crt_AymAH.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/39/c5/114719_crt_AymAH.jpg"},"